---
title: Crushed Beets & Whole Wheat Spaghetti with Lemony Ricotta, Hazelnuts & Basil Oil
description: Get ready to be shocked by this recipe. Yes—beets, caramelized red onion, lemon, and garlic really do create an insanely delicious pasta sauce. Drizzled with garlic-basil oil and sprinkled with toasted hazelnuts, this dish will certainly push you out of your recipe rut. Don’t be skimpy with that fresh ricotta— its creaminess brings the whole dish together!
